name: Buddy
description: Buddy is a friendly, outgoing dog who loves to play fetch and go for walks. He gets along well with children and other dogs.

name: Lucy
description: Lucy is a sweet and gentle dog who loves nothing more than snuggling up on the couch with her humans. She is good with children and other pets.

name: Max

name: Charlie
